name: Explosive Power, flat 10
description:
Today's session requires you to complete an increasing tempo effort, after first producing a short, high powered interval. To replicate the demands of a fast and flat 10min effort, keep your cadence 3-5rpm higher than what you would normally find comfortable. The session finishes with a high cadence 10min sub-threshold effort.
